@startuml Navigation_Flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor #E1F5FE
    BorderColor #01579B
}

[*] --> SplashActivity

SplashActivity --> LoginActivity : Not Logged In
SplashActivity --> MainActivity : Already Logged In

LoginActivity --> MainActivity : Login/Guest Mode

MainActivity --> RealAIDetectionActivity : Environment Recognition
MainActivity --> DocumentCurrencyActivity : Document Reading
MainActivity --> VoiceCommandActivity : Voice Command
MainActivity --> FindItemsActivity : Find Items
MainActivity --> TravelAssistantActivity : Travel Assistant
MainActivity --> InstantAssistanceActivity : Instant Assistance
MainActivity --> GestureManagementActivity : Gesture Management
MainActivity --> SettingsActivity : Settings

RealAIDetectionActivity --> MainActivity : Back
DocumentCurrencyActivity --> MainActivity : Back
VoiceCommandActivity --> MainActivity : Back
FindItemsActivity --> MainActivity : Back
TravelAssistantActivity --> MainActivity : Back
InstantAssistanceActivity --> MainActivity : Back
GestureManagementActivity --> MainActivity : Back
SettingsActivity --> MainActivity : Back

MainActivity --> [*] : App Exit

note right of MainActivity
  Java File:
  MainActivity.java
  Central navigation hub
  Language switching available
  Emergency button always accessible
end note

@enduml
